---
title: Brazilian Roasted Sweet Potato 'Veijoada' with Fragrant Braised Cabbage
description: Fragrant spices paired with beans, tender sweet potatoes and braised cabbage make for a simple stick-to-you-ribs veggie stew.  You'll love the deep warm flavours that compplement this dish.
